tariff simulator:
----------------

reads input file with call minutes and a tariff and returns the total cost of the bill


sample usage:
./tariff.py data lobo : calculates the bill for month bill/data with tariff lobo
./tariff.py data best : calculates the best tariff for month bill/data
./tariff.py all best : calculates the best tariff for all monthly bills in bill/
./tariff.py all lobo : calculates the total bill for tariff lobo with all monthly bills in bill/
